content:
Certainly! Below is a sample HTML email template designed to promote a new product. This template includes a header, product showcase, call-to-action button, and a footer with social media icons and contact information. It's structured to be visually appealing and mobile-responsive.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Product Launch</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: white;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 100px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 10px 0 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .product-section {
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .product-section img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
        .product-section h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
        }
        .product-section p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555555;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #555555;
        }
        .footer a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #555555;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer img {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .cta-button {
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Company Logo">
            <h1>Introducing Our Latest Innovation!</h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Product Section -->
        <div class="product-section">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/550x300" alt="New Product Image">
            <h2>Revolutionary Product Name</h2>
            <p>Experience the future with our new product that blends cutting-edge technology with unparalleled design.</p>
            <a href="https://example.com/product" class="cta-button">Learn More</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Follow us on</p>
            <a href="https://facebook.com"><img src="https://via.placeholder.com/24/fb_icon" alt="Facebook"></a>
            <a href="https://twitter.com"><img src="https://via.placeholder.com/24/twitter_icon" alt="Twitter"></a>
            <a href="https://instagram.com"><img src="https://via.placeholder.com/24/insta_icon" alt="Instagram"></a>
            <p>Contact us: contact@example.com | +123 456 7890</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

### Key Features:
- **Header:** Contains the company logo and a catchy tagline.
- **Product Section:** Showcases the new product with an image and a brief description.
- **Call-to-Action Button:** Encourages viewers to click for more information.
- **Footer:** Includes social media icons and contact information.

This template is designed to be simple yet effective, with responsiveness for mobile devices. Customize the links, images, and text as needed for your specific product and brand identity.
